HEADWORD: Rhizogen
<hw>Rhiz"o*gen</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>One of a
proposed class of flowering plants growning on the roots of other plants
and destitute of green foliage.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rhizoid</ent>⟦br⟧
